acute severe ulcerative colitis (ASUC)
ASUC = 6 BM + , HR > 100, FEVER, 10.5 hb, ESR > 30 should be admitted for intravenous steroids, intravenous methylprednisolone 60 mg/d
to induce remission. Patients should have stool testing to rule out C. difficile infection. flexible sigmoidoscopy within 72 hours, and preferably within 24 hours of admission
to assess the endoscopic severity of inflammation and obtain biopsies to evaluate for cytomegalovirus (CMV) colitis. 

